p: SD = Standard Deviation; RSD = Relative Standard Deviation; TSFA = Total Saturated Fatty Acid; TMUFA = Total Monounsaturated Fatty Acid; TUFA = Total Unsaturated Fatty Acid; TEFA = Total Essential Fatty Acid; TNEFA = Total Non-Essential Fatty Acid; O/L = Oleic/Linoleic Ratio; TPUFA = Total Polyunsaturated Fatty Acid; n-6/n-3 = linoleic (n-6)/α–linolenic (n-3) Ratio, P/S = Polyunsaturated Fatty Acid/Saturated Fatty Acid.
